body.query:
query me {
  me {
    id
    firstName
    lastName
    username
    email
    phoneNumber
    intlPhoneNumber
    status
    isPhoneVerified
    isEmailVerified
    isBVNVerified
    isNINVerified
    isWalletFunded
    countryCode
    connectionHash
    photo {
      id
      path
      width
      height
      __typename
    }
    kycStage
    userTypeId
    pages {
      id
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
